rows.label: tlk70000054_01_msg0001
rows.name:
We call ourselves the "resistance army"
but we're actually just starting out.
Not so much an army as a club, really.

rows.label: tlk70000054_01_msg0002
rows.name:
We may be small, but we've
got all sorts. Invidians,
Iirans, Gulans, Superbians...

rows.label: tlk70000054_01_msg0003
rows.name:
There's plenty of folks in Invidia
who'd readily put us to use as
a mercenary strike force.

rows.label: tlk70000054_01_msg0004
rows.name:
But who's to say that won't strain
tensions with Iira and Superbia?
We've worked hard to get this far.

rows.label: tlk70000054_01_msg0005
rows.name:
As lieutenant, I'm not about to let my
troops be used to fight their homelands.
We've only got one goal - defeat Metsu.
